      <title>SEC说，Stablecoins不是需要注册的证券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/sec-says-stablecoins-aren-t-securities-that-require-registration</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Stablecoin发行人和交易所周五在该机构的工作人员确定资产通常不是证券之后获得了证券交易委员会的提升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-04/sec-says-stablecoins-aren-t-securities-that-require-registration</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 04 Apr 2025 22:26:33 GMT</pubDate>
